OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779887471
OL,3,CNASA unveils plans for permanent moon
OL,4,Cbase as stepping stone to Mars
OL,6,FNASA's ambition - and timetable - for
OL,7,Fpeople to live and work on the moon is
OL,8,Fbecoming has become much clearer as
OL,9,FITV News' North America Correspondent
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FNASA has unveiled plans to put a
OL,13,Fpermanent base on the moon that would
OL,14,Festablish humanity's first lunar
OL,15,Foutpost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
