FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779887471
OL,3,CNASA unveils plans for permanent moon
OL,4,Cbase as stepping stone to Mars
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference to
OL,7,Funveil the plans, NASA Administrator
OL,8,FJared Isaacman thanked US president
OL,9,FDonald Trump as he announced the first
OL,10,Fof three missions will be on Amazon
OL,11,Fbillionaire Jeff Bezos' Blue Origin
OL,12,FMark I Endurance lander, set to launch
OL,13,Fthis autumn.
OL,15,FOpening the conference, Isaacman said:
OL,16,F"America returns to the moon again and
OL,17,Fthis time to stay."
OL,19,F"The moon base will be America's and
OL,20,Fhumanity's first outpost on another
OL,21,Fcelestial world," he said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
