PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779887471
OL,3,CNASA unveils plans for permanent moon
OL,4,Cbase as stepping stone to Mars
OL,6,F"Every mission, crewed and uncrewed,
OL,7,Fwill be a learning opportunity as we
OL,8,Freturn to the lunar surface, build the
OL,9,Finfrastructure to stay, and master the
OL,10,Fskills required to live and operate in
OL,11,Fone of the most demanding and
OL,12,Fdangerous environments imaginable.
OL,14,F"We will go for the science, for all
OL,15,Fwe stand to gain from an economic and
OL,16,Ftechnological perspective, for the
OL,17,Finnovations that will make life better
OL,18,Fhere on Earth, and to prepare for
OL,19,Fwhere we will inevitably go next.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
