OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779887471
OL,3,CNASA unveils plans for permanent moon
OL,4,Cbase as stepping stone to Mars
OL,6,F"We are grateful for President Trump's
OL,7,Fleadership, the bipartisan commitment
OL,8,Ffrom Congress, our industry and
OL,9,Finternational partners, and the
OL,10,Fdedicated NASA workforce whose
OL,11,Fexpertise enables us to achieve the
OL,12,Fnear-impossible."
OL,14,FNASA said the moon base will be built
OL,15,Fover time, starting with near-term
OL,16,Ftechnology demonstrations, robotic
OL,17,Fmissions, and early experiments.
OL,26,@tD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
