PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779887471
OL,3,CNASA unveils plans for permanent moon
OL,4,Cbase as stepping stone to Mars
OL,6,FThe second base mission will fly cargo
OL,7,Fto the lunar surface aboard while a
OL,8,Fthird will deliver payloads "chosen
OL,9,Fthrough open competition, as well as
OL,10,Finternational partners".
OL,12,FBoth missions are targeted to launch
OL,13,Fbefore the end of 2026.
